name: Twilight Ninja Food Catcher
description:
An easy going game that you need to catch foods, it may be simple but sometimes simple is better; you need to catch the foods to move on to the next level.

Each level gets a little harder, but nothing too hard, most will be able to win this in 1 or 5 tries and that isn't a bad thing at all.

So for any fan of the show or just someone looking for an easy going game, try this one out.
